rl_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Honey: The Prophet uses honey to treat upset stomach","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \"My brother has diarrhea.\" The Prophet said, \"Give him honey to drink.\" The man gave him honey to drink and he said, \"I gave it to him but his diarrhea only\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10425,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/17\/muhammad-three-things-liar\/","url_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Whoever says this about the Prophet is a liar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Masruq reported: I asked Aisha, \u201cO mother, did Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, see his Lord?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhat you said makes my hair stand on end! Know that if someone tells you one of three things, he is a liar. Whoever tells you that Muhammad saw his\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/13\/prophet-liked-sweets-honey\/","url_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sweets: The Prophet liked naturally sweet food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to like sweets and honey. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5115 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u062d\u0650\u0628\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e 5115 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0637\u0639\u0645\u0629 \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/muhammad-no-better-akhlaq-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":3},"title":"Aisha on Muhammad: None had better character than the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cNo one had better character than the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. No one from his companions or his family called upon him but that he would say: I am at your service. For this reason,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6770,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/prophet-describes-wahy\/","url_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wahy: The Prophet describes his revelations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Al-Harith ibn Hisham asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how do you receive revelation?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSometimes it is revealed like the ringing of a bell. This form of revelation is the hardest of all, but this hardship subsides once\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/prophet-rebukes-hafsa-safiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":22323,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Pride: The Prophet rebukes Hafsa for insulting Safiyyah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: Safiyyah heard that Hafsa called her \u201cthe daughter of a Jew,\u201d so Safiyyah started crying. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered while she was crying and he said, \u201cWhat makes you cry?\u201d Safiyyah said, \u201cHafsa called me the daughter of a Jew.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u062